latestPosts.caption:
feeling magnetic!!! ☁️🫶🏼✨ just a lil message for my girlies who are going THROUGH it right now… 

there have been days where i thought i’d never see my self worth again, self love would forever be a distant memory and my spark would never shine quite like it used to… but little by little, day by day, we came right through the other side. 🌈

if there is anything that i have learnt over the past year, it’s that when everything in your life feels like it is falling apart, it’s so something even better can fall into place… i can’t wait to see you over here. 🌈✨

-

making friends in your 20’s can be difficult. if you’re a lil bit lost, struggling to navigate the highs and lows of what we call the “20’s” then join our community! we have group chats and daily facetime lives which are a safe space for all the girly wirly’s. no judgement, nothing is off limits. just girls supporting girls 🥹☁️🎀

#friendship #girlhood #healing #healingjourney #navigatinglife #justagirl
